=== Timeline

    - *Months 1–6*: Establish pacing, optimize symptom management, identify triggers
    - *Months 6–12*: Implement disease-modifying strategies (immune modulation, hormones, microbiome)
    - *Year 1–2*: Assess trajectory - stable? improving? worsening?
    - *Year 2–5*: Continued optimization; some patients achieve significant recovery or remission

